%% State — Voucher
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> scheduled: Admin tạo voucher<br/>validFrom > now

  scheduled --> active: Đến validFrom<br/>(và isActive=true)

  [*] --> active: Tạo voucher<br/>không có validFrom

  active --> exhausted: usedCount >= usageLimit
  active --> expired: now > validUntil
  active --> disabled: Admin set isActive=false

  disabled --> active: Admin set isActive=true<br/>(còn hạn, còn lượt)

  exhausted --> [*]
  expired --> [*]
  disabled --> [*]

  note right of active
    isValid(orderValue) → {valid:true}
    computeDiscount() → discount > 0
  end note
